defaultUNISON is the UK’s largest public services union representing over 
default1.1 million workers in local government, health, education, police and justice and the voluntary and community sector delivering public services. UNISON members work directly for contracting public authorities and for 
defaultprivate, community and voluntary sector service providers. 
